description: Penthouse living at it's finest! This expansive 1 bed PLUS DEN offers an open, light filled living area complete with TWO PRIVATE DECKS and 1 GARAGE PARKING SPACE.  Built in 2016, awash in natural light and featuring a flexible floor plan with a glass enclosed office/den complete with custom electronic shades for privacy when needed. The kitchen incorporates breakfast bar seating with quartz countertops and is outfitted with custom cabinetry maximizing storage.  A convenient powder room is nicely appointed.  The primary suite features two closets and an en suite bath with glass shower stall.  Step outside onto the back deck for dinner and head up to the expansive private roof deck to enjoy sunset views.  W/D in unit and basement storage round out the offerings.  Located just across from numerous new development projects, notably Washington Village which will usher in new energy and excitement with 650+ new residential units, 45k+ sqft of retail space and an open 7500+ sqft green space.
